import React from 'react'
import { useState } from 'react'

import { classes } from './styles'
import Input from './Input'
import { Container, Avatar, Button, Paper, Grid, Typography, TextField } from '@mui/material'

const Auth = () => {

  const [isSignedup, setIsSignedup] = useState(true)

  return (
    <>
    <Container component='main' sx={classes.container}>
      <Paper>
        <Grid container>
          {isSignedup && 
          <>
            <Input name='firstName' label='First Name' type='text'></Input>
          </>
          }
          {/* <Input name='email' label='Email' type='email'></Input> */}
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
      
    </Container>

  </>
  )
}

export default Auth
